Name: aluminium oxide, metallurgical, import from Northern America | aluminium oxide, metallurgical | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/24:Manufacture of basic metals/242:Manufacture of basic precious and other non-ferrous metals/2420:Manufacture of basic precious and other non-ferrous metals
Description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/21547/documentation

This dataset represents the amount of imported primary aluminium oxide metallurgical from Northern America to EU27 & EFTA. The import value is valid for 2015 and includes all  imports, independently whether used within the importing region, or re-exported.

The activity starts at the factory gate with the product ready for transport.

This activity includes the transport from the exporting region (including transport within the region) to EU27 & EFTA.
